Package: because
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Estimation of Causal Effects
Version: 1.2.3
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Achaz", "von Hardenberg",
      email = "achaz.hardenberg@unipv.it",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for specifying and fitting Bayesian Structural Equation Models
    using JAGS or NIMBLE. The 'because' package allows causal inference in complex ecological and 
    evolutionary analyses, accounting for phylogenetic uncertainty (through the because.phybase extension), spatial autocorrelation, 
    and other covariance structures.
SystemRequirements: JAGS (>= 4.0.0)
